metadata.name: SS.Sweet and Sour
metadata.description:
Only summer vibes, summer feelings, joy, happiness.

"Dear Friend,

Don`t wait for tomorrow, enjoy the moment right now.

Do not live in in the past or in the future. Live right now. 

We have limited hours on this planet. 

Enjoy your journey right now, don`t miss it!

Taste, feel, touch, express yourself through all you can. 

Do something good for people, for planet, for your family, for yourself right now. 

Feel yourself. Be yourself.

Feel the life...."

Sincerely yours,

Sweet and Sour
